Invocation Name: my african safari
des:
Adventure in Kruger National Park.

Go on adventures with unexpected twists and turns including going for a bush walk, stalking lions, helping archaeologists with a dig, making paint, creating rock art, doing some smelting, and getting chased by a rhino.

2 areas, 8 stories, 26 endings. 
Over an hour of pick your path adventures.
